WEBVTT

00:00:20.330 --> 00:00:24.525
 TODAY IS JANUARY FIFTEEN, NINETEEN NINETY-SEVEN.

00:00:24.784 --> 00:00:27.275
SURVIVOR: Mindl Melamed.

00:00:27.754 --> 00:00:31.528
THE LAST NAME AT BIRTH WAS Semetski.

00:00:31.887 --> 00:00:34.143
INTERVIEWER: DAVID Karlen.

00:00:34.521 --> 00:00:40.877
THE INTERVIEW IS TAKEN IN BROOKLYN, NEW YORK, UNITED STATES OF AMERICA, AND THE LANGUAGE IS yidish.

00:00:43.279 --> 00:00:49.010
mir ruft men DAVID Karlen: kuk. alef. reysh. lamed.

00:00:49.185 --> 00:00:50.900
ayen. lange nun.

00:00:51.177 --> 00:00:53.618
haynt iz yanuARY der fuftseter,

00:00:53.674 --> 00:00:56.300
toyznt nayn hundert nayntsik zibn.

00:00:56.779 --> 00:01:00.519
ikh nem an intervyu bay di froy Mindl Melamed,

00:01:00.930 --> 00:01:02.949
geborene Semetski.

00:01:03.192 --> 00:01:06.746
der intervyu kumt for in Bruklin, Nyu-York,

00:01:07.191 --> 00:01:09.648
fareynikte shtatn oyf Amerike.

00:01:13.097 --> 00:01:14.728
vi ruft men aykh?

00:01:14.515 --> 00:01:17.820
mikh ruft men Mindl Melamed.

00:01:17.957 --> 00:01:20.026
kent ir zogn dos in di oysyes?

00:01:19.459 --> 00:01:24.380
M.I.N.D.E.L.

00:01:25.551 --> 00:01:26.928
un ayer familye?

00:01:26.597 --> 00:01:32.570
M.E.L.A.M.E.D.

00:01:34.225 --> 00:01:37.730
vos iz gevezn ayer familye beys ir zayt geborn gevorn?

00:01:37.043 --> 00:01:40.260
mayn familye iz geven Semetski.

00:01:40.215 --> 00:01:41.373
kent ir ⟨z-⟩...

00:01:40.283 --> 00:01:46.470
S.E.M.E.T.S.K.I.

00:01:47.944 --> 00:01:49.625
ir hot gehat andere nemen?

00:01:49.648 --> 00:01:50.435
NO.

00:01:50.695 --> 00:01:52.326
ir hot gehat tsunemenishn?

00:01:52.131 --> 00:01:53.131
NO.

00:01:54.289 --> 00:01:56.071
ven zayt ir geborn gevorn?

00:01:55.707 --> 00:02:01.040
ikh bin geborn gevorn in nayntsn zeks un tsvontsik, dem zekstn JanuVar.

00:02:01.090 --> 00:02:02.569
vi alt zayt ir yetst?

00:02:02.878 --> 00:02:04.770
eyn un zibetsik yor.

00:02:04.532 --> 00:02:06.399
vu zayt ir geborn gevorn?

00:02:06.017 --> 00:02:08.188
in shtetele Lipkan

00:02:08.683 --> 00:02:11.140
bin ikh geborn gevorn. UNK

00:02:11.299 --> 00:02:13.301
vu iz dos, di shtetl?

00:02:12.936 --> 00:02:14.415
in Basarabye.

00:02:14.472 --> 00:02:16.536
ikh bin aleyn a Basaraber.

00:02:16.536 --> 00:02:18.750
geborn bin ikh in Lipkan.

00:02:18.505 --> 00:02:20.760
velkhe melukhe iz dos geven demlt,

00:02:20.760 --> 00:02:22.396
ven ir zayt geborn gevorn?

00:02:22.673 --> 00:02:24.337
vos heyst "melukhe"?

00:02:25.002 --> 00:02:30.300
velkhe, vu zayt ir gevezn, velkh- velkhe iz dos geven, d- di sh- d- di melukhe? velkhe melukhe iz dos gevezn?

00:02:32.562 --> 00:02:33.990
ikh veys...

00:02:32.730 --> 00:02:34.970
es iz geven Rusland? ⟨vos⟩ iz geven UNK?

00:02:33.990 --> 00:02:36.170
a! s'iz geven Rumenye.

00:02:36.170 --> 00:02:39.410
Rumenye. kh'hob nit farshtanen vos ir hot gezogt.

00:02:39.514 --> 00:02:42.427
dertseylt undz vegn ayer lebn

00:02:42.703 --> 00:02:44.992
in der tsayt biz der milkhome,

00:02:45.707 --> 00:02:49.170
vegn dem lebn fun ayer shtetl vu ir hot gelebt,

00:02:49.170 --> 00:02:50.539
vos s'iz geven far a shtetl, dem

00:02:50.539 --> 00:02:53.126
gezelshaftlekhn, kulturn lebn

00:02:53.166 --> 00:02:58.222
fun di yidishe bafelkerung un oykh, nokh, nit-yidishe oykh, ⟨oybe s'iz⟩ meglekh,

00:02:58.752 --> 00:03:01.676
biz onheyb fun UNK religyezn lebn.

00:03:01.676 --> 00:03:03.405
dertseylt alts vos ir veyst vegn dem.

00:03:03.405 --> 00:03:05.107
biz der milkh- ⟨tsayt fun⟩ milkhome.

00:03:03.409 --> 00:03:07.210
geven iz bay undz a yidishe shtot.

00:03:07.847 --> 00:03:11.131
Lipkan iz geven zeyer a bavust shtetl.

00:03:11.256 --> 00:03:12.768
same yidn.

00:03:13.483 --> 00:03:14.928
geven shiln,

00:03:15.070 --> 00:03:17.450
geven a yidisher teater,

00:03:17.450 --> 00:03:19.830
a ukraynisher teater.

00:03:20.740 --> 00:03:23.451
mir z- ikh bin nokh geven zeyer yung.

00:03:24.013 --> 00:03:28.951
kh'hob in lebn, kon ikh zogn, gornisht farbrakht in di yunge yorn.

00:03:29.768 --> 00:03:31.722
tsores iz geven

00:03:31.722 --> 00:03:34.010
merert vifl m'hot gedarft.

00:03:34.577 --> 00:03:37.330
bay undz iz gev- hot zikh gefirt a shtub.

00:03:37.330 --> 00:03:39.178
s'iz geven a pekarnye.

00:03:40.129 --> 00:03:42.114
s'hot gearbet mentshn.

00:03:43.183 --> 00:03:44.527
mayn tate

00:03:44.550 --> 00:03:46.872
iz geven a guter balebos.

00:03:46.879 --> 00:03:49.387
er hot lib gehat tsu tun mitsves.

00:03:50.389 --> 00:03:56.356
er hot khasene gemakht etlekhe yesoymes. mayn mame's a shvester, gedenk ikh di khasene.

00:03:56.987 --> 00:03:59.259
gemakht a groyse khasene

00:03:59.552 --> 00:04:01.414
mit a y- yosem,

00:04:01.414 --> 00:04:04.524
vos er hot gearbet bay undz, an arbetorer.

00:04:04.750 --> 00:04:06.921
er hot zikh farlibt in Khanen.

00:04:07.112 --> 00:04:09.410
geven zeyer a sheyn meydl.

00:04:09.760 --> 00:04:13.552
 mayn mame hot gehat a yerushe-shtub funem zeydn.

00:04:14.352 --> 00:04:17.841
der zeyde hot ge- di mame hot gegibn, mitn tatn,

00:04:17.841 --> 00:04:22.963
Khanen un Vigdern a PRESENT di shtub, zey zoln hobn vu tsu voynen,

00:04:22.963 --> 00:04:25.618
vayl zey zenen geven tsvey yesoymim;

00:04:25.776 --> 00:04:27.750
zey hobn keynem nit gehat.

00:04:28.830 --> 00:04:31.772
dos iz geven mayn mame's shvester,

00:04:31.772 --> 00:04:33.940
di yingere fun ir.

00:04:34.045 --> 00:04:36.630
s'iz geven nokh tsvey meydlekh:

00:04:36.846 --> 00:04:38.274
Kh⟨aye-So⟩re,

00:04:38.854 --> 00:04:41.109
Kha- ⟨iz zi⟩ Beyle.

00:04:41.487 --> 00:04:43.840
zey hobn gearbet bay undz,

00:04:43.840 --> 00:04:45.463
flegn tsilyen beygl,

00:04:45.520 --> 00:04:47.263
helfn farkoyfn.

00:04:47.263 --> 00:04:51.060
zey hobn geholfn in shtub tsu di kinder oykhet.

00:04:52.843 --> 00:04:55.040
vifl kinder zaynen geven in ayer sh-...?

00:04:53.822 --> 00:04:56.330
mir ze'mir geven zeks kinder.

00:04:55.881 --> 00:04:58.271
kent ir ibertseyl- ver s'iz gevezn?

00:04:57.332 --> 00:05:00.590
yo. s'iz geven eyn bruderl...

00:05:00.590 --> 00:05:03.755
dos el- di eltste iz geven mayn shvester Lide.

00:05:03.812 --> 00:05:05.679
zi voynt in Yisroel.

00:05:05.837 --> 00:05:07.991
di tsveyte bin ikh geven.

00:05:08.520 --> 00:05:11.383
der driter iz geven Y- Yosele,

00:05:11.676 --> 00:05:14.140
a yingele, zeyer a sheyner.

00:05:14.865 --> 00:05:17.525
der ferter iz geven Dudele.

00:05:18.325 --> 00:05:21.103
der fifter iz geven Hershl.

00:05:22.965 --> 00:05:29.120
un... n- neyn, der ferder Hershl, un der fifter Borye.

00:05:30.053 --> 00:05:35.390
der bruder iz geshtorbn do in Amerike, Borye iz geshtorbn do in Amerike.

00:05:35.390 --> 00:05:37.264
di ile kinder zenen

00:05:37.264 --> 00:05:40.910
oysgeshtorbn in lager far hunger un far kelt.

00:05:40.617 --> 00:05:42.771
vegn dem veln mir dertseyln shpeter.

00:05:41.680 --> 00:05:44.120
vet men dertseyln shpeter.

00:05:42.810 --> 00:05:45.166
ye. dertseylt itster vegn ayer lebn...

00:05:45.865 --> 00:05:48.390
vos zol ikh aykh dertseyln fun mayn lebn?

00:05:49.594 --> 00:05:51.800
ikh bin nokh geven yung.

00:05:52.058 --> 00:05:53.841
kh'bin gegan in a shCHOOL,

00:05:54.150 --> 00:05:56.742
in a yidisher shCHOOL, zeyer veynik,

00:05:57.137 --> 00:06:00.101
vayl kh'hob nit uspeyet; ikh bin geven a kranke.

00:06:00.394 --> 00:06:05.855
in der ershter tsayt hob ikh zeyer, geven krank. fun elef yor on hob ikh gekont geyn in shCHOOL.

00:06:06.250 --> 00:06:09.433
kh'bin gegan a dray, fir yor in Tarbus.

00:06:09.658 --> 00:06:13.430
m'hot gelernt yidish. ikh hob es shoyn fargesn.

00:06:14.620 --> 00:06:18.170
kh'hob mikh tsunoyfgekumen mit sheyne meydelekh, shkheynim,

00:06:19.632 --> 00:06:22.005
tsunoyfgekumen mit di kinder.

00:06:22.652 --> 00:06:27.658
vayter, fun far der milkhome ⟨hob i-⟩ veys ikh nit vos tsu dertseyln. got hot geholfn...

00:06:30.550 --> 00:06:34.071
s'iz ey- eyn yingele bay undz geshtorbn.

00:06:36.709 --> 00:06:37.867
un den...

00:06:39.257 --> 00:06:41.056
zeyer krank geven.

00:06:41.417 --> 00:06:44.190
veys nit vos tsu dertseyln fun far der milkhome.

00:06:44.910 --> 00:06:48.042
in, vu ir hot gelebt, ⟨az ir zayt⟩ gegangen in shul...

00:06:46.665 --> 00:06:49.696
mir ho'mir gelebt in Lipkan.

00:06:48.805 --> 00:06:51.451
in shul, ven ir zayt gegangen, zikh gelernt...

00:06:50.293 --> 00:06:55.906
ven ikh bin gegan in shul hob ikh ge- mit kinder zikh tsunoyfgekumen. m'hot gelernt yidish.

00:06:56.537 --> 00:07:00.918
me fleg kumen tsu mir in shtub arayn; m'hot bay mir gemakht di LESSONS.

00:07:02.055 --> 00:07:03.416
⟨veys nit⟩...

00:07:02.325 --> 00:07:06.554
ayere eltern hobn gel- g- bakumen tsaytungen, geler- gel-...?

00:07:05.278 --> 00:07:10.388
yo. mayn foter fleg ile fraytik, flegn zikh tsunoyfkumen etlekhe shkheynim

00:07:10.388 --> 00:07:15.260
tsu undz in shtub arayn. er fleg zikh oyfzetsn oyfn tish... dos iz vos ikh gedenk...

00:07:15.403 --> 00:07:19.121
un zey zenen gezesn oysgezetst, vu m'hot gehat a plats,

00:07:19.121 --> 00:07:21.770
un er fleg zey leyenen bikhlekh,

00:07:21.770 --> 00:07:23.360
yidishe bikher.

00:07:23.360 --> 00:07:26.096
meystn teyl yidish, un oyf rumenish

00:07:26.305 --> 00:07:27.868
fleg er zey leyenen.

00:07:28.228 --> 00:07:34.308
zey hobn shoyn nisht gekont dervartn dem tog fun fraytik, az me zol araynkumen, zikh avekzetsn bay Zeydlen,

00:07:34.308 --> 00:07:37.217
un me zol hern vi azoy er leyent di bikher.

00:07:38.050 --> 00:07:41.858
s'iz geven bay undz arbetorer, zeyer oreme mentshn.

00:07:42.572 --> 00:07:46.666
s'hot gearbet bay undz a arbetorer, der zun iz do in Amerike.

00:07:46.791 --> 00:07:49.700
er bagegnt zikh mit mir zeyer oft.

00:07:49.700 --> 00:07:51.560
er iz geven zeyer orem.

00:07:52.174 --> 00:07:57.365
 er fleg a mol aroysganvenen a bisl holts fun der pekarnye aheymtsunemen, oystsuheytsn.

00:07:59.076 --> 00:08:04.910
dos hot men undz dertseylt, di arbetorers, dertseylt mayn tatn. zogt er, "oyf,

00:08:05.404 --> 00:08:10.170
oyf Bentsienen zolt ir mir gornit zogn. vos er tut, fardint er zikh.

00:08:10.197 --> 00:08:12.671
se hart mikh nit az er nemt es."

00:08:13.808 --> 00:08:17.447
mir ho'mir zeyer geholfn a sakh mentshn, mayne eltern:

00:08:17.571 --> 00:08:22.530
kranke, alte. di mame fleg preglen ayngemakhtsn,

00:08:22.530 --> 00:08:26.273
un me fleg vinter kumen mit a gloz betn a bisl,

00:08:26.447 --> 00:08:30.221
me zol, gibn farn krankn, er zol zikh mekhaye zayn.

00:08:30.767 --> 00:08:35.401
s'iz geven bay undz nisht keyn... mir ze'mir nit geven keyn gevirim,

00:08:35.424 --> 00:08:39.000
nor s'hot zikh gefirt bay undz a balebatishe shtub.

00:08:39.000 --> 00:08:40.881
ver s'iz arayngekumen,

00:08:40.881 --> 00:08:44.430
hungerik iz er nit aroysgegan. dos iz vos ikh gedenk.

00:08:45.145 --> 00:08:48.078
fleg peysekh praven dem seyder,

00:08:48.078 --> 00:08:51.078
geven finef, zeks yesoymelekh bay undz

00:08:51.321 --> 00:08:52.783
tsum seyder.

00:08:53.076 --> 00:08:56.242
mayn tatn's a mume, zi iz geshtorbn,

00:08:56.383 --> 00:09:00.270
un der man iz geven aleyn. er hot zikh zeyer geplagt.

00:09:00.383 --> 00:09:04.950
oyf ile yontoyvim fleg er n- flegn zey nemen di kinder tsun undz.

00:09:05.445 --> 00:09:11.413
un di kinder zenen geven meystn teyl bay undz vi bay zey in der heym, vayl di mamen hobn zey nisht gehat.

00:09:12.297 --> 00:09:14.063
dos iz vos ikh gedenk.

00:09:14.929 --> 00:09:17.580
ir gedenkt vegn di, vegn di

00:09:15.380 --> 00:09:16.526
vos...

00:09:17.580 --> 00:09:20.525
religye? ayer foter fleg geyn in shul?

00:09:19.485 --> 00:09:25.270
ma- y- o, ye. mayn tate fleg geyn in shil, ober er hot gehat a nomen in shil.

00:09:25.270 --> 00:09:30.921
m'hot gezogt, "Zeydl beker⟨s⟩, epes hot men eyn mol bay im oysgekoyft di markhe"... markhe?

00:09:31.416 --> 00:09:32.422
mayrev.

00:09:33.880 --> 00:09:34.785
UNK

00:09:35.128 --> 00:09:40.803
hot men oysgekoyft. mayn tate hot nit gevolt arayngeyn in der shil; er hot gevolt ibergeyn in a anderer,

00:09:40.803 --> 00:09:45.972
nor azoy vi er hot gehat fir pletser in shil dort, fun zayn tatn, fun zayn bobe.

00:09:46.317 --> 00:09:51.444
iz ⟨er⟩, hot men, iz men gekumen tsun undz in shtub arayn un m'hot im ibergebetn,

00:09:51.444 --> 00:09:56.470
un m'hot im gezogt, er zol geyn in shil arayn. er iz a por vokhn nisht gegan tsu zey;

00:09:56.560 --> 00:09:58.629
ayer foter flegt oft geyn in shul?

00:09:56.577 --> 00:09:59.575
er iz gegan in a anderer shil. a?

00:09:59.057 --> 00:10:00.924
er flegt oft geyn in shul?

00:10:00.087 --> 00:10:03.321
er fleg, yo. mayn foter fleg oft geyn in shil.

00:10:02.466 --> 00:10:05.190
ale tog, oder er fleg geyn nor oyf shab-...?

00:10:03.799 --> 00:10:09.660
er fleg geyn kimat ile oyfdernakht, iz er gegan in shil arayn, vayl bay undz hobn gearbet arbetorers

00:10:09.660 --> 00:10:11.926
un er iz geven a balebos.

00:10:12.152 --> 00:10:16.415
den hot gevoynt bay undz mayn tatn's a shvester, di eltste.

00:10:16.523 --> 00:10:18.322
⟨Masye⟩ hot zi geheysn.

00:10:18.379 --> 00:10:20.651
zi iz geven a komunistke.

00:10:22.513 --> 00:10:29.291
zi hot zikh zeyer geboret far Rusland un hot ongeton undz zeyer a sakh tsores far mayn tatn UNK

00:10:29.415 --> 00:10:30.736
zeyer a sakh.

00:10:30.736 --> 00:10:32.565
unter ile yontoyvim

00:10:32.672 --> 00:10:35.146
fleg men kumen un im arestirn

00:10:35.254 --> 00:10:38.744
un a- aveknemen; mir ho'mir nit gevust vu er iz.

00:10:38.744 --> 00:10:40.887
me fleg im hargenen un shlogn,

00:10:40.887 --> 00:10:43.044
un zi fleg zikh oysbahaltn.

00:10:43.810 --> 00:10:47.736
di letste tsayt iz zi antlofn keyn Yas, keyn Rumenye,

00:10:48.113 --> 00:10:49.997
vayl m'hot zi gevolt shisn.

00:10:50.357 --> 00:10:55.121
zi hot gefirt di ile papirn un di ile tsetlen, vos zey flegn klebn oyf di,

00:10:55.121 --> 00:10:57.253
oyf di slupes in droysn.

00:10:58.575 --> 00:11:00.833
un ales iz geven bay undz

00:11:00.833 --> 00:11:05.218
in kamer. veyst s'heyst "in kamer"? in, vu s'ferd iz geshtanen.

00:11:05.730 --> 00:11:11.073
dortn unter der pol iz geven oysgegrobn a grub... dos iz vos ikh gedenk...

00:11:11.417 --> 00:11:15.640
un in dem grub iz geven arayngeleygt ale bikher

00:11:15.754 --> 00:11:20.658
un ale tsetlen vos m'hot gedarft klebn oyf di slupes in droysn.

00:11:20.715 --> 00:11:22.751
un ayer foter hot dos alts erloybt?

00:11:22.070 --> 00:11:28.890
un mayn tat-... zey hobn gevoynt in der shtub, nor in a anderer zayt; er hot nit gevust vos zey tuen dort.

00:11:30.250 --> 00:11:35.420
un oyf ile yontoyvim hot men mayn tatn arestirt, un er hot zeyer a sakh fun ir gelitn,

00:11:35.667 --> 00:11:40.403
nor oysgibn hot er zi nisht gevolt, vayl s'iz dokh geven a shvester.

00:11:42.180 --> 00:11:44.671
vayter, vos zol ikh aykh dertseyln?

00:11:45.150 --> 00:11:49.784
vos zol ikh dertseyln fun, fun far der milkhome? ikh gedenk nit azoy alding.

00:11:48.475 --> 00:11:53.143
ir ⟨v-,⟩ ir gedenkt, ayere elter⟨n⟩ flegn geyn in shul? ikh meyn...

00:11:51.934 --> 00:11:56.327
m- yo, mayn mame un mayn tate. voden? m'iz gegan in shil arayn.

00:11:56.327 --> 00:12:00.670
m'hot gehaltn di yontoyvim. s'hot zikh gefirt bay undz a sheyne shtub.

00:12:01.435 --> 00:12:06.949
peysekh, rosheshone, ⟨me, vos s'iz⟩ faran⟨, un⟩ purim flegn kumen di

00:12:06.949 --> 00:12:09.511
tsigayner shpiln in shtub arayn.

00:12:09.771 --> 00:12:13.920
m'iz, ze- mir ho'mir gefirt zeyer a sheyn lebn.

00:12:14.631 --> 00:12:19.639
s'hot undz baym rumen gornisht gefelt, akhuts di tsores durkh der TЁTye

00:12:19.639 --> 00:12:21.280
vos mir ho'mir gehat.

00:12:21.280 --> 00:12:25.408
vayter hot undz gornit gefelt. mayn tate iz geven a guter balebos.

00:12:25.802 --> 00:12:30.962
s'hot gearbet zeks arbetorers in pekarnye. s'hot gearbet a sheygets bayn furl.

00:12:30.962 --> 00:12:33.080
s'iz geven a meydl in shtub.

00:12:33.080 --> 00:12:37.206
s'hot undz gornit gefelt. mir ho'mir fun keyn tsores baym rumen

00:12:37.206 --> 00:12:41.110
nisht gevust, nor dos eyne vos der tate hot gelitn.

00:12:42.745 --> 00:12:44.123
az,

00:12:44.230 --> 00:12:45.759
ir zayt gevezn...

00:12:46.288 --> 00:12:51.142
ir zayt ge- ir gedenkt, ayere eltern flegn geyn in teater?

00:12:50.187 --> 00:12:54.233
o, yo! ikh bin oykh geven. mir ze'mir oykhet geven.

00:12:52.954 --> 00:12:54.365
dertseylt undz vegn...

00:12:54.233 --> 00:12:57.770
s'hot geshpilt zeyer a sheyne zakh, vi azoy,

00:12:57.770 --> 00:13:01.722
vifl me darf hobn mitsves, un vifl neveyres.

00:13:01.813 --> 00:13:05.851
hot der tate gezogt der mamen, "lomir geyn mit di kinder in teater arayn."

00:13:05.851 --> 00:13:09.570
di mame hot dokh nit gevolt lozn di arbetorers aleyn in shtub.

00:13:09.643 --> 00:13:12.830
fleg zi zogn, "nem di kinder un gey."

00:13:12.830 --> 00:13:14.970
ikh bin nokh geven a kleyn meydele,

00:13:15.094 --> 00:13:18.159
un mayn shvesterl iz elter fun mir mit tsvey yor.

00:13:18.182 --> 00:13:21.604
m'hot undz ongeton, tsugekumen in a fyaker,

00:13:21.604 --> 00:13:24.639
un m'hot undz tsugefirt tsum teater mit mayn tatn.

00:13:24.848 --> 00:13:27.561
dos gedenk ikh, vi ⟨zi⟩ hot gezungen,

00:13:27.561 --> 00:13:30.562
"oy, oy, oy, nokh tsvey matones feln mir."

00:13:31.311 --> 00:13:35.518
dos gedenk ikh zeyer. geven etlekhe mol in yidishn teater.

00:13:35.518 --> 00:13:37.965
in di kinos fleg men undz nemen.

00:13:37.965 --> 00:13:39.600
geven a sheyne...

00:13:38.112 --> 00:13:40.569
oyf, in kino ⟨f-⟩ iz geven oyf yidish?

00:13:40.403 --> 00:13:43.972
s'iz gev-..., oyf yidish, neyn. oyf rumenish iz dos geven.

00:13:43.972 --> 00:13:48.984
kh'bin geven, mir ho'mir nokh farshtanen rumenish. geven kinder, m'hot geredt rumenish.

00:13:48.984 --> 00:13:53.141
flegn araynkumen tsun undz koynim un m'hot geredt nor rumenish.

00:13:53.468 --> 00:13:58.700
iz oyf rumenish geven di kinos. s'iz geven zeyer a sakh kinos, teaters.

00:13:58.716 --> 00:14:00.853
zeyer sheyn geven in shtetl.

00:14:01.956 --> 00:14:05.766
ayer foter hot, tsugehert tsu velkhe nit iz,

00:14:05.766 --> 00:14:09.307
organizatsyes, ikh meyn tsienistishe, Bundishe...?

00:14:07.137 --> 00:14:11.721
ikh gedenk, ikh gedenk nit... in tsienistish iz mayn tate geven.

00:14:11.659 --> 00:14:13.239
vos flegt er ton?

00:14:12.351 --> 00:14:17.240
yo, er fleg, far Yisroel hot men geredt; di gantse tsayt fleg ikh hern.

00:14:17.240 --> 00:14:20.631
flegn zikh tsunoyfkumen di bekers tsun undz in shtub arayn.

00:14:20.772 --> 00:14:25.350
m'iz gegan fun der shil, flegn... u- undz ho'mir gevoynt lebn der shnayderisher shil...

00:14:25.350 --> 00:14:28.539
flegn zey araynkumen, zikh avekzetsn baym tish.

00:14:28.539 --> 00:14:32.696
di mame fleg aroyfshteln sheyne zakhn oyfn tish, gebeksn.

00:14:32.702 --> 00:14:36.450
un flegn zitsn un redn fun tsienistishe zakhn.

00:14:36.550 --> 00:14:41.826
meystn teyl hot er, er iz geven shtark a farbrenter far, far Yisroel UNK.

00:14:42.490 --> 00:14:45.352
er hot untergehaltn mit gelt?

00:14:43.738 --> 00:14:49.690
er iz geven epes in a ORGANIZATION, nor vu veys ikh nisht. zet oys, in der tsienistisher,

00:14:49.690 --> 00:14:53.200
far derfar vos zey flegn redn di gantse tsayt fun dem.

00:14:54.117 --> 00:14:59.308
zogt mir, hot ir gefilt epes, antisemitizm in Rumenye ven ir hot gelebt...?

00:14:57.998 --> 00:15:01.839
efsher iz geven. ikh bin nokh geven yung; kh'hob nit farshtanen.

00:15:02.318 --> 00:15:07.478
s'iz geven. di Kuzistn flegn kumen tsu der makht, flegn zey kumen in shtetl arayn,

00:15:07.478 --> 00:15:11.756
un shisn, un, un, trefn yidn oyf der gas, shlogn.

00:15:11.756 --> 00:15:13.804
dos gedenk ikh; s'iz geven.

00:15:14.518 --> 00:15:16.700
oder, azoy...

00:15:15.227 --> 00:15:17.330
⟨un⟩ far di Kuzistn?

00:15:17.316 --> 00:15:18.709
far di Kuzistn,

00:15:18.709 --> 00:15:20.368
gedenk nisht gornisht.

00:15:20.695 --> 00:15:22.120
gedenk nit.

00:15:21.640 --> 00:15:27.641
dortn zaynen gevezn, dortn zaynen gevezn nor yidishe bafelkerung, oder s'zaynen gevezn...?

00:15:26.803 --> 00:15:29.277
in dem MIDDLE, in der shtot

00:15:29.352 --> 00:15:32.130
iz geven di yidishe shtiber

00:15:32.625 --> 00:15:38.060
un yidishe bafelkerung. arum un arum hobn gevoynt nor goyim, arum der shtot.

00:15:38.060 --> 00:15:40.941
dos shtetl iz geven, kon men zogn, a yidishs.

00:15:40.941 --> 00:15:43.520
vu m'iz gegan, hot men geredt yidish.

00:15:43.560 --> 00:15:47.570
fleg zikh tsunoyfkumen di ORGANIZATIONS, nor oyf yidish geredt.

00:15:48.032 --> 00:15:53.004
az m'iz shoyn tsunoyfgekumen fun UNK shtotishe, flegn zey redn oyf rumenish.

00:15:55.018 --> 00:15:57.510
dos, dos iz vos ikh gedenk.

00:15:56.875 --> 00:16:01.968
vi hot zikh batsien di bafelkerung, nit-yidishe vos ⟨hobn⟩ gelebt arum di shtetl, tsu

00:16:01.968 --> 00:16:02.960
di yidn?

00:16:02.764 --> 00:16:09.350
zeyer veynik iz men zikh tsunoyfgekumen mit zey. di yidishe mentshn zenen nisht tsunoyfgekumen zikh mit di goyim.

00:16:09.075 --> 00:16:12.410
ir hot gelernt in a yidishe shul, oder UNK?

00:16:10.898 --> 00:16:14.824
in Tarbus hob ikh gelernt, in a yidishn Tarbus.

00:16:14.948 --> 00:16:18.750
dort hot men gelernt yidish, oder kh'hob zeyer veynik farkhapt,

00:16:18.981 --> 00:16:21.455
vayl ikh bin geven zeyer a kranke.

00:16:22.153 --> 00:16:27.290
iz hob ikh gelernt a bisl yidish, in gantsn dray, fir yor, nisht merert.

00:16:27.290 --> 00:16:30.264
un den hot zikh ongehoybn di milkhome, hob ikh shoyn

00:16:30.304 --> 00:16:31.698
ales farloyrn.

00:16:31.823 --> 00:16:35.141
ir hot gelebt unter Rumenye bizn fertsikstn yor?

00:16:34.708 --> 00:16:35.579
yo.

00:16:35.890 --> 00:16:38.347
⟨shoyn⟩ in fertsiktn yor zayt ir shoyn gevezn...

00:16:36.649 --> 00:16:41.418
in fertsik- in eyn un fertsikstn yor iz dokh arayn... yo, in fertsikstn yor.

00:16:38.758 --> 00:16:40.085
in fertsikstn.

00:16:40.429 --> 00:16:46.025
az s'zaynen gekumen di Sovyetn, hot dos, ayer lebn hot zikh gebitn, ayer foter's UNK?

00:16:44.648 --> 00:16:49.755
zeyer a sakh gebitn zikh. azoy vi di rusn zenen arayngekumen,

00:16:49.980 --> 00:16:54.460
iz in dem novnt... zey zenen gekumen fraytik bay tog,

00:16:54.460 --> 00:16:56.167
zenen zey arayn tsu undz...

00:16:56.680 --> 00:17:03.019
un in dem novnt hot gedarft bay undz zayn a bris; dos kleyne bruderl mayns iz geboyrn gevorn.

00:17:03.767 --> 00:17:09.329
geven ales in shtub tsugegreyt, geshtelt der tish... un a mol hot men gemakht in shtub dem bris...

00:17:10.517 --> 00:17:17.517
un den hot geton a kum oyfdernakht; m'hot zikh gedarft tsunoyfkumen, iz men zikh shoyn nisht tsunoyfgekumen, far derfar vos

00:17:17.517 --> 00:17:20.466
m'hot gedarft geyn bagegenen di khaveyrim.

00:17:21.587 --> 00:17:26.860
m'iz akegngelofn di tanken. bay undz in der gas hot zikh opgeshtelt eyn tank.

00:17:26.860 --> 00:17:28.490
zey hobn zikh opgeshtelt.

00:17:28.759 --> 00:17:32.904
un eyn yidisher bokher hot gezen durkh der vinde

00:17:33.113 --> 00:17:36.500
az se brenen likht fraytik

00:17:36.500 --> 00:17:38.050
in a yidisher shtub.

00:17:38.050 --> 00:17:39.708
m'hot dokh oyf shabes

00:17:39.708 --> 00:17:42.422
gebentsht likht; m'hot gefirt yidish.

00:17:43.052 --> 00:17:48.955
tut er a makh tsu mayn tatn... mayn tate iz geven azoy heyzerik funem shrayen dem hura

00:17:48.955 --> 00:17:50.826
az er hot nit gekont redn...

00:17:51.186 --> 00:17:52.985
tut er tsun im a makh,

00:17:53.211 --> 00:17:56.563
"oy, hot ir gemakht a shlekhtn shidekh mit undz.

00:17:56.839 --> 00:17:59.364
ir't zen vu ir gefint zikh."

00:18:00.315 --> 00:18:04.890
un meyn hot er gornit, er, m'hot dokh moyre gehat tsu redn epes.

00:18:06.340 --> 00:18:07.450
un den

00:18:07.450 --> 00:18:10.586
hot men geton a nem tsunoyf ile bekers,

00:18:11.217 --> 00:18:12.640
un m'hot zey gezogt

00:18:12.640 --> 00:18:15.463
az in der heym ken keyner nit arbetn.

00:18:15.874 --> 00:18:17.623
me darf makhn

00:18:18.287 --> 00:18:22.078
a kom-, vi azoy? a ARTEL'.

00:18:20.565 --> 00:18:21.639
UNK

00:18:22.455 --> 00:18:25.621
a ARTEL', az me zol arbetn ale tsuzamen.

00:18:25.982 --> 00:18:30.245
m'vet tsunoyfnemen di tsukernikes, di vos zey makhn di CANDIES,

00:18:31.146 --> 00:18:32.895
un di bekers,

00:18:33.272 --> 00:18:36.281
un nokh epes eyn ORGANIZATION... ikh gedenk nisht vos...

00:18:36.281 --> 00:18:39.020
un m'vet makhn, se zol zayn eyns.

00:18:39.128 --> 00:18:41.754
me darf oyskloybn a predsyedatel,

00:18:42.132 --> 00:18:44.179
ver s'vet zayn der eltster.

00:18:44.179 --> 00:18:46.300
hot men oysgekloybn mayn tatn.

00:18:46.890 --> 00:18:52.640
mayn tate iz geven a gelernter, un zeyer a kluger, un a bavuster bay undz in shtet⟨l⟩.

00:18:53.978 --> 00:19:00.114
m'hot im oysgekloybn, er zol zayn predsyedatel. di bekers hobn gehat fil fardrosn oyf dem,

00:19:01.707 --> 00:19:06.932
vayl zey hobn gezen az, m'heybt im tsu fil oyf, hobn zey es nisht gekont laydn.

00:19:07.275 --> 00:19:09.665
er fleg makhn ORGANIZATIONS.

00:19:10.161 --> 00:19:12.956
me fleg zikh tsunoyfkumen oyf sobranyes,

00:19:14.211 --> 00:19:15.680
un er fleg

00:19:15.680 --> 00:19:18.862
aroystretn der ershter un redn.

00:19:20.944 --> 00:19:23.950
di pekarnye hot mayn tate gefirt.

00:19:24.606 --> 00:19:27.469
zey hobn im zeyer gevolt aynzetsn,

00:19:28.217 --> 00:19:32.058
vayl zey hobn gezen az er iz tsu a groyser natshalnik far zey.

00:19:33.330 --> 00:19:38.575
oder s'hot zey gornit geholfn; vi azoy zey zenen im gekrokhn in di pa- PAPERS arayn,

00:19:38.575 --> 00:19:41.070
azoy hot er zey fardreyt dem kop.

00:19:41.447 --> 00:19:45.055
un m'hot gemakht a sheyn lebn bay di rusn oykhet.

00:19:45.055 --> 00:19:47.367
far vos? vayl mayn tatn's lebn

00:19:47.367 --> 00:19:49.420
iz geshtanen ayngeshtelt,

00:19:49.463 --> 00:19:52.180
oyf tsvontsik yor, yedn tog.

00:19:54.627 --> 00:19:56.940
den, m'hot opgelebt dos yor.

00:19:56.940 --> 00:19:58.957
der tate iz geven predsyedatel

00:19:59.993 --> 00:20:02.370
un di arbetorers hobn gearbet.

00:20:02.370 --> 00:20:05.060
dank got, keyn tyurme hot er nisht gekhapt.

00:20:05.376 --> 00:20:07.175
hot er gekhapt di milkhome.

00:20:07.772 --> 00:20:14.094
zogt mir, ⟨a-⟩ zaynen gevezn di be- di, in artel zaynen gevezn nor yidn, oder zaynen gevezn nit-y-...?

00:20:11.232 --> 00:20:12.086
yo.

00:20:13.088 --> 00:20:18.004
s'iz geven kristn oykhet. di arbetorers vos zey hobn gearbet in di pekarnyes,

00:20:18.004 --> 00:20:22.042
di hobn gedarft arbetn in ARTEL' oykh in di pekarnyes.

00:20:22.285 --> 00:20:24.710
iz geven d-, di arbetorers UNK...

00:20:23.382 --> 00:20:25.755
un di balebatim fun andere k⟨UNK⟩?

00:20:24.710 --> 00:20:28.846
un di andere balebatim hobn gearbet arbetorers, poshete,

00:20:28.846 --> 00:20:31.341
un mayn tate iz aroys der natshalnik.

00:20:33.203 --> 00:20:35.540
azoy iz dos geven, dos lebn.

00:20:35.540 --> 00:20:37.837
m'hot gedarft lebn nor oyf geneyve.

00:20:38.470 --> 00:20:40.774
 zogt mir, in ayer shtot,

00:20:41.050 --> 00:20:43.642
az di, s'zaynen gekumen di Sovyetn,

00:20:43.969 --> 00:20:46.696
zaynen gevezn ge- faln az me hot genumen,

00:20:46.737 --> 00:20:50.578
yidn aroysgeshikt, oder VOOBSHCHE, bikhlal aroysgeshikt?

00:20:49.234 --> 00:20:54.847
yo, yo. dos iz geven dem tsveytn tog vos di rusn zenen arayngekumen.

00:20:55.647 --> 00:20:57.311
fun ile kleytn...

00:20:57.874 --> 00:21:02.829
bay undz iz geven, di tsigaynerishe gas iz geven same yidishe kleytn:

00:21:03.038 --> 00:21:05.074
groyse magazinen

00:21:05.147 --> 00:21:06.778
fun skhoyres,

00:21:06.801 --> 00:21:08.500
fun esnvarg,

00:21:08.657 --> 00:21:10.693
zeyer groyse balebatim.

00:21:11.239 --> 00:21:13.556
m'iz oyfgeshtanen in der fri:

00:21:13.556 --> 00:21:16.616
ale tirn un fentster zenen geven ofn,

00:21:17.415 --> 00:21:21.290
alding oysgeramt, glaykh s'iz dort keyn zeykher nit geven.

00:21:21.921 --> 00:21:27.821
ales avekgenemen. dem andern tog iz shoyn keyn kap ga- kerosin nit geven vu tsu koyfn.

00:21:28.097 --> 00:21:31.494
azoy iz geven ales opgeCLEANt fun ile gevirim.

00:21:31.494 --> 00:21:35.198
di kleytn, ales ofn: di vindes, di tirn.

00:21:35.198 --> 00:21:38.131
nisht geven tsu vemen a vort tsu redn. m'hot zey...

00:21:37.125 --> 00:21:38.840
ver hot, ⟨, bay⟩ zey tsugenumen?

00:21:38.273 --> 00:21:42.360
di rusn zenen ge- bay nakht arayn mit mashinen.

00:21:42.360 --> 00:21:45.501
m'hot ales oysgegruzet fun di shtiber

00:21:45.501 --> 00:21:47.790
un es avekgeshikt keyn Rusland.

00:21:48.347 --> 00:21:51.580
s'iz di, di r- rusishe froyen

00:21:51.580 --> 00:21:53.825
hobn zikh ongeton di nakht-hemder

00:21:54.135 --> 00:21:55.558
un zenen gegangen

00:21:55.558 --> 00:21:58.660
in gas; zey hobn gemeynt az s'iz kleydlekh.

00:21:58.660 --> 00:21:59.917
zey hobn genemen

00:21:59.923 --> 00:22:03.295
di ⟨OLIVE⟩s, maslines,

00:22:03.295 --> 00:22:06.279
opgekokht kompot; zey hobn gemeynt az s'iz flomen.

00:22:06.387 --> 00:22:08.425
zey hobn nisht gevust vos tsu tun,

00:22:08.425 --> 00:22:11.814
vayl zey hobn es in Rusland nisht gezen un nit gegat.

00:22:13.643 --> 00:22:16.134
dos, dos gedenk ikh vos s'iz geven.

00:22:16.056 --> 00:22:21.079
bay aykh zaynen gevezn, in di yidishe, ir gedenkt efsher, zaynen gevezn yidishe,

00:22:21.321 --> 00:22:25.736
fun di tsienistishe organizatsyes, zaynen gevezn fi- onfirers, oder...?

00:22:25.320 --> 00:22:28.290
⟨⟩, dos veys ikh nit. ikh veys nisht.

00:22:28.071 --> 00:22:34.292
s'iz gevezn az m'hot, m'hot arestirt, di Sovyetn zaynen gekumen, hobn zey arestirt vemen fun di yidishe bafelkerung, neyn?

00:22:28.290 --> 00:22:29.871
ikh denk az s'iz geven.

00:22:34.534 --> 00:22:36.131
aroysgeshikt?

00:22:34.686 --> 00:22:38.150
aroysgeshikt hot men ⟨dokh⟩ di mentshn vos m'hot

00:22:38.150 --> 00:22:42.021
fun di kleytn ales h- hot men avekgenemen un m'hot nit gevust vu.

00:22:42.043 --> 00:22:44.250
ir hot gekent eynike fun zey?

00:22:42.415 --> 00:22:44.504
m'hot zey ile av-... yo, yo.

00:22:44.250 --> 00:22:46.154
ir gedenkt zeyere familyes?

00:22:44.504 --> 00:22:46.980
mi- i-... neyn.

00:22:47.123 --> 00:22:50.500
ikh gedenk, m'hot z⟨i⟩ gerufn Sh⟨UNK⟩ Koyen.

00:22:50.500 --> 00:22:52.786
Koyen efsher iz geven di familye.

00:22:52.962 --> 00:22:55.580
dos iz a groyse kleyt geven,

00:22:55.580 --> 00:22:58.727
vos mayn tate fleg koyfn dort far der pekarnye

00:22:59.020 --> 00:23:02.743
mel, tsuker, vos m'hot gedarft. dos gedenk ikh.

00:23:02.952 --> 00:23:04.194
UNK

00:23:03.137 --> 00:23:05.560
nor vayter gedenk ikh nisht.

00:23:04.622 --> 00:23:09.780
ir gedenkt, zay- zaynen zey ibergeblibn lebn? dos veyst ir nit? zey hobn nit ge- ir hot zey nit getrofn?

00:23:07.238 --> 00:23:09.915
NO, m'hot zey avekgeshikt keyn Sibir.

00:23:09.921 --> 00:23:14.690
vi azoy zey zenen gelign in di betn, azoy hot men zey aroysgenemen un avekgeshikt,

00:23:14.781 --> 00:23:18.555
un ⟨o-⟩ keyn hemd afile nisht gelozt nemen, gornisht.

00:23:18.460 --> 00:23:20.259
vi hot ir zikh dervust vegn dem?

00:23:20.164 --> 00:23:20.910
ha?

00:23:20.738 --> 00:23:22.031
vi hot ir...

00:23:20.910 --> 00:23:23.111
m'hot zikh dervust dem andern tog;

00:23:23.168 --> 00:23:25.038
m'iz aroysgegan in gas arayn,

00:23:25.038 --> 00:23:26.903
iz keyn mentsh nisht geven.

00:23:26.903 --> 00:23:29.456
di gantse gas iz geven oyfgehoybn

00:23:29.698 --> 00:23:32.847
un avekgeshikt, un oysgeramt di kleytn:

00:23:32.922 --> 00:23:35.011
gornisht geven in di kleytn.

00:23:35.011 --> 00:23:37.711
m'hot shoyn nisht gehat vu tsu koyfn a shtikl broyt,

00:23:37.711 --> 00:23:40.080
ver s'hot gornit gehat in shtub.

00:23:41.072 --> 00:23:48.204
hot ir gehert far der milkhome vegn Daytshland, vegn di Natsis, Natsistn, vegn Hitlern?

00:23:47.367 --> 00:23:49.660
ikh gedenk, ikh hob,

00:23:49.660 --> 00:23:53.199
bin gegan tsum Prut. mir ze'mir zikh gegan bodn.

00:23:53.323 --> 00:23:55.910
gedenk ikh, lebn der zhandarmerye

00:23:55.910 --> 00:23:59.125
iz geshtanen a akht furlekh mit mentshn,

00:23:59.125 --> 00:24:01.468
vos zenen shoyn geven antlofene.

00:24:02.115 --> 00:24:05.079
oder ver, vos, hobn mi- hob ikh nit gevust;

00:24:05.203 --> 00:24:08.750
bin ⟨no⟩kh geven tsu yung zikh tsu visn fun azoyne zakhn.

00:24:09.388 --> 00:24:14.107
kh'gedenk, s'iz geshtanen dortn etlekhe furlekh mit mentshn, sa- yidn,

00:24:14.502 --> 00:24:19.283
ongegruzet, mit di kinder, mit zek, ongeleygt dort UNK. zet oys, zey hobn nokh

00:24:19.283 --> 00:24:22.580
gekont mitnemen a bisl zakhn mit zikh.

00:24:23.007 --> 00:24:24.510
dos gedenk ikh.

00:24:24.508 --> 00:24:27.190
zaynen, fun vanen zey zaynen gelofn v⟨eyst ir nit⟩?

00:24:25.791 --> 00:24:28.410
fun vanen zey zenen gelofn veys ikh nisht.

00:24:28.187 --> 00:24:30.678
un dos iz alts geven far der milkhome nokh?

00:24:29.930 --> 00:24:32.130
dos iz far der milkhome geven.

00:24:37.722 --> 00:24:41.951
vi iz forgekumen, vi hot ir zikh dervust, vi hot zikh ongehoybn di milkhome?

00:24:42.379 --> 00:24:46.102
ven s'hot zikh ongehoybn di milkhome dem tsvey un tsvontsiktn JUNE,

00:24:47.323 --> 00:24:49.880
geven a fir a zeyger far tog,

00:24:50.665 --> 00:24:52.341
mir ze'mir nokh geshlofn,

00:24:52.341 --> 00:24:53.865
gelign in di betn,

00:24:54.107 --> 00:24:57.425
hot ongehoybn flien snaradn ibern kop.

00:24:57.448 --> 00:24:59.380
mir ho'mir gevoynt

00:24:59.406 --> 00:25:00.733
in Lipkan.

00:25:01.482 --> 00:25:05.627
in Lipkan iz geven di grenets keyn ⟨Radahuts⟩.

00:25:05.717 --> 00:25:08.039
⟨Radavuts⟩ iz geven Rumenye.

00:25:09.497 --> 00:25:11.111
un mir hobn gevoynt

00:25:11.134 --> 00:25:14.570
in Lipkan, un s'iz geven a brik aribertsugeyn.

00:25:15.808 --> 00:25:21.050
dortn zenen geven shoyn di daytshn mit di Rumener, tsuzamen,

00:25:21.192 --> 00:25:23.076
un zey hobn ongehoybn

00:25:23.115 --> 00:25:25.980
tsu shisn iber, keyn Lipkan,

00:25:25.980 --> 00:25:28.374
in der shtot arayn, mit snaradn.

00:25:29.410 --> 00:25:32.590
un di snaradn zenen gefloygn ibern kop.

00:25:32.590 --> 00:25:35.557
m'hot nit gekont afile fun der shtub aroysgeyn,

00:25:35.557 --> 00:25:38.077
un shtiber hobn shoyn ongehoybn brenen.

00:25:38.775 --> 00:25:40.704
geshosn hot men geshosn

00:25:40.704 --> 00:25:42.599
in mitn der shtot.

00:25:42.893 --> 00:25:46.684
dort hot men gevust az se voynen di, di komunistn.

00:25:49.002 --> 00:25:53.730
un den hot der tate ayngeshpant dos fe- f- di ferd

00:25:53.777 --> 00:25:56.449
un er hot undz ile aroyfgevarfn oyf der fur,

00:25:56.449 --> 00:25:58.952
un m'hot zikh genemen antloyfn fun Lipkan.

00:25:59.970 --> 00:26:03.811
m'iz antlofn finef un tsvontsik kilometer keyn Britshan.

00:26:04.628 --> 00:26:07.820
in Britshan hot mayn tate gehat a gutn-bruder,

00:26:07.820 --> 00:26:10.410
un er hot undz geton a loz arayn tsun im,

00:26:10.686 --> 00:26:14.243
un er iz geforn krik az er zol nemen dem bagazh.

00:26:14.243 --> 00:26:16.226
er hot gemeynt, er vet nokh epes nemen.

00:26:16.226 --> 00:26:19.790
er iz tsugekumen, hot er gezen, undzer shtub ⟨iz,⟩ brent,

00:26:20.203 --> 00:26:24.264
un s'iz shoyn alding oysgeramt, iz er krik avek keyn Britshan.

00:26:24.777 --> 00:26:27.820
ze'mir avek keyn Britshan. dort vu mir ze'mir geven

00:26:27.820 --> 00:26:29.861
iz geven punkt bayn veg,

00:26:29.861 --> 00:26:32.432
vos di komunistn hobn ongehoybn loyfn...

00:26:33.197 --> 00:26:35.505
di Kuzistn, di Kuzistn

00:26:35.505 --> 00:26:38.506
hobn ongehoybn loyfn oyf tsu rabeven di yidn.

00:26:38.547 --> 00:26:40.718
tsu hargenen, tsu rabeven.

00:26:40.858 --> 00:26:43.460
hot der khaver mayn tatn's gezogt,

00:26:43.491 --> 00:26:45.664
"Zeydl, nem di kinder

00:26:45.664 --> 00:26:47.082
mit UNK Rosye

00:26:47.082 --> 00:26:49.746
un gey avek in der un der shil arayn.

00:26:50.005 --> 00:26:54.082
ir tort nisht zayn do bayn veg." er hot mitgegibn zayn vayb oykhet,

00:26:54.173 --> 00:26:56.006
un di shv- shviger.

00:26:56.080 --> 00:26:59.618
mir zenen avekgegan ot dort, me zol nisht zayn bayn veg.

00:27:00.231 --> 00:27:02.419
mir ze'mir geven in der shil

00:27:02.948 --> 00:27:04.760
a fir, finef tog.

00:27:05.344 --> 00:27:07.633
iz ongekumen a prikaz

00:27:07.639 --> 00:27:09.467
az ile Lipkaner

00:27:09.467 --> 00:27:13.168
zoln aroysgeyn oyf der tolike fun der pozharne,

00:27:13.984 --> 00:27:16.104
aza plats a groys.

00:27:17.578 --> 00:27:21.878
blaybn hot men moyre gehat, vayl, m'hot gezogt, tomer vet blaybn

00:27:21.878 --> 00:27:24.457
emetser fun di Lipkaner in Britshan,

00:27:25.105 --> 00:27:26.753
vet men undz shisn.

00:27:26.792 --> 00:27:29.216
ver hot gegebn aza bafel, aza prikaz?

00:27:28.058 --> 00:27:29.830
di Rumener.

00:27:29.914 --> 00:27:33.250
di Rumener hobn shoyn bafelt.

00:27:34.150 --> 00:27:37.519
den iz men aroysgegan yeder oyf der tolike,

00:27:37.812 --> 00:27:39.540
ile Lipkaner.

00:27:39.583 --> 00:27:43.542
s'iz a gantse shtot mit mentshn geven, zeyer a sakh mentshn.

00:27:44.730 --> 00:27:47.306
un der eybershter hot undz gegibn a regn,

00:27:47.380 --> 00:27:51.060
az m'iz geshtanen iber di knies in vaser.

00:27:51.767 --> 00:27:54.073
un m'hot undz ile tsunoyfgenemen.

00:27:55.243 --> 00:27:59.877
un s'iz geven a tsvelef Rumener mit a akht daytshn,

00:27:59.884 --> 00:28:02.680
un m'hot undz ongehoybn traybn oyf di vegn.

00:28:03.023 --> 00:28:05.025
aroysgetribn fun Britshan,

00:28:05.048 --> 00:28:08.720
gegan in vaser un in blote biz in di knies arayn.

00:28:09.030 --> 00:28:12.530
di kinder hobn geveynt, hungerike geven

00:28:12.928 --> 00:28:15.082
zeyer, yeder eyner.

00:28:16.725 --> 00:28:20.360
un m'hot undz getribn iber tol un iber berg,

00:28:21.214 --> 00:28:25.038
durkh di derfer; nisht gelozt undz arayngeyn durkhn dorf,

00:28:25.062 --> 00:28:30.250
az emetser, oder bahaltn zikh ergets, oder nemen ergets a shtikl broyt.

00:28:30.327 --> 00:28:32.531
oyf di felder undz getribn.

00:28:32.942 --> 00:28:38.926
toyznter kilometers iz men gegangen. di hitsn ⟨in⟩ zenen geven zeyer groyse;

00:28:39.591 --> 00:28:41.780
s'hot gebrent di erd.

00:28:42.055 --> 00:28:45.840
keyn trunk hot keyner nit gehat a kap vaser tsu nemen.

00:28:46.138 --> 00:28:48.427
di kinder, ile hobn geveynt.

00:28:50.340 --> 00:28:52.207
un m'hot undz getribn

00:28:53.125 --> 00:28:59.470
in der Ukrayne arayn. tsugetribn hot men undz biz MOGILЁV-PODOL'SK, keyn Molev.

00:28:58.761 --> 00:29:00.915
mir'n zikh opshteln oyf a vayle

00:29:00.972 --> 00:29:04.280
tsu makhn an iberrays, tsu beytn, be-

00:29:02.119 --> 00:29:04.200
yo. yo.

00:29:04.280 --> 00:29:05.150
dem TAPE.
